_sText:
This map is for 64 players,
Each player gets an AWP & knife & a hand gun.
There is a frozen river in the middel were each team can get a cross, there is two ways up and down on both sides of the river,
all roof tops you can get on, heavy tree cover for snipper and a few boxes for cover. a barn were you can snip from in many spots, a boat frozen in the middel were you can also snip from.

this is a very fun snipper map but becareful if you dont watch your back in this map you will get a suprize :)

you can vist me at www.etkgamers.com
Changes:
 Added water with damage
 Added Ice that breaks
 Added heilo sounds when crossing the ice
 Added a working .Nav for bots
